      </a>
      <a href="YOUR_LIBRARY_LINK_HERE" target="_blank" class="start-link-item">
        Explore the full library <span>↗</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="start-here-right">
    <h3>Reading should feel like something.</h3>
    <p>Not a chore. Not homework. Not something you do to seem interesting at dinner parties. Just — something real, something that stays.</p>
    <p>That's what we're here for.</p>
    <a href="index.html" class="btn-cream">Start exploring</a>
  </div>
</div>

